reviewText: I bought this box set because I collect Anime & I already have the previous box sets of Bleach. This box set was much better than the previous one, it had lots of intense battles with the Espadas. The story with Aizen's plan is further along. One of my favorite battles was when Ichigo was fighting against Ulquiorra in his fully Hollified state.
